The next group of manufacturers of fake invoices includes those who have some connection with the defendants.
For example, Ivan Kubatov was the plaintiff of the Ukrainian manager of the Delta Trio SL with a fictitious headquarters in Budapest, which dealt with the trade of fuels and vehicles.
